---
// Hero — light theme with the isometric capability diagram cropped from the mockup on the right.
---

<section class="relative bg-[#F9FBFE] py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-screen-2xl px-6 sm:px-10 lg:px-16 xl:px-20 mx-auto w-full">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Left Content -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 text-center lg:text-left">
        <p class="!text-[12.6px] tracking-[0.15em] text-[#2563EB] uppercase font-medium">
          Engineering Expertise. Technology Innovation. Real Impact.
        </p>

        <h1 class="!text-[40px] sm:!text-[48px] lg:!text-[56px] xl:!text-[64px] leading-[1.1] text-[#0B1220]">
          Engineering Smarter<br />
          <span class="text-[#2563EB]">Digital Solutions</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="!text-[18px] text-[#5A5A5A] max-w-xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 leading-relaxed">
          NextStep Engineering combines engineering expertise with cutting-edge
          technology to deliver engineering software, Product Lifecycle
          Management (PLM), cloud engineering, AI &amp; analytics, custom
          software development, DevOps, and Industrial IoT solutions that help
          organizations innovate and achieve sustainable growth.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start mt-2">
          <a
            href="/#services"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 !text-[15.4px] font-medium text-white bg-[#2563EB] rounded-xl hover:bg-[#1d4fd1] transition-colors"
          >
            Explore Our Solutions
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="w-4 h-4">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 !text-[15.4px] font-medium text-[#0B1220] border border-[#0B1220]/25 rounded-xl hover:bg-[#0B1220]/5 transition-colors"
          >
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-4 h-4">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6.75 3v2.25M17.25 3v2.25M3 18.75V7.5a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 7.5v11.25m-18 0A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75m-18 0v-7.5A2.25 2.25 0 015.25 9h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 11.25v7.5" />
            </svg>
            Book a Consultation
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: isometric capability diagram (cropped from the Home.png mockup) -->
      <div class="w-full max-w-[480px] sm:max-w-[560px] mx-auto">
        <img
          src="/hero-diagram.webp"
          alt="NextStep capability diagram: AI & Analytics, Cloud Engineering, DevOps, Industrial IoT, Software Development, PLM, Digital Transformation"
          class="w-full h-auto"
          loading="eager"
          decoding="async"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
